								<h2>About</h2>
								<p>Taris is an open source project aimed at helping ad tech developers create simple, efficient, and effective BLE (Bluetooth Low Energy / Beacon) marketing solutions. We work to prvide the groundwork for such solutions, enabling firms to focus on innovation and personalization, opposed to underlying communications.</p>
								<p>Our platform contains a unique method to register BLE devices, allowing developers to leverage tags to target large groups of BLE devices at once. With Taris, one can target consumers based on their microlocation, their real time actions, or their demographics.</p>
								<p>Taris is released under the MIT license, giving developers free reign to not only innovate, but monetize. Use Taris to create innovative mediabuying solutions for advertisers and their brand partners, from self-serve platforms to fully functional RTB exchanges.</p>
							</div>
						</li>
						
