								<p>All documentation is found within our API, powered by Apiary. Updates will routinely be posted within the API, not on this site. With popular demand, we may start pushing notifications through Twitter for ease of access. If this is a service you request, please let us know.</p>
							
								<p>Source code is hosted on Github. Code submits can either be made through email, or by contacting us directly on Github. All submits become property of Taris once approved, but you may modify the platform and use it in a commercial environment as long as it follows the terms found in our license.</p>
